translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いつかを思い出すな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It reminds me of some time.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「せ、戦争……でしょうか。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: W-War... could it be?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いえ、散々やってはいるんですけど……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: No, we've been fighting plenty already though...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「魔軍……ウザい。数多すぎ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The demon army... such a pain. There are just too many.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 作戦って言っても……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Even if you call it a strategy...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「んー、まあ普通の手段じゃ、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hmm, well, with normal means,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: どうにもならないようにも思えるけどねえ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It seems like we can’t do much about it...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あむっ……むぐ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: *munch*... *muffle*...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あーもう、折女さん……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ah, really, Orihime-san...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: こんな時までおはぎを……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Bringing ohagi even at a time like this...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「どうであっても……梵天丸と共に往くのみ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: No matter what happens... I will go forth with Bontenmaru.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 地獄であろうと……修羅場であろうと」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Whether it’s hell... or a battlefield of carnage.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「さあ、幕は大詰めだな。くくく、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Now then, the curtain is drawing to its climax. Hehehe,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: カオスマスターめ。何を言い出すかな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: you Chaos Master. I wonder what you’ll say now.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ふむ、あむ……んん、甘い……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hmm, *munch*... mmm, sweet...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: この城のパティシエ、いい腕を……あむ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The patissier of this castle has skilled hands... *munch*

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ALICE様……我らをお見守りください……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lady ALICE... please watch over us...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: はああああ、ALICE様ぁ……！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Haaaaa, Lady ALICE...!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: （サチコはどうした……？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: (What happened to Sachiko...?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: またどこかで迷子になったか……）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Did she get lost somewhere again...?)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「なんぞ、また無茶を言い出すのでは
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Don’t tell me you’re about to say something reckless again.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あるまいな……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It can’t be...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「きっとすごい事だよ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It’s surely something amazing.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: だっておとーさんだもん！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Because it’s Dad after all!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ったく、もう慣れたわ……ん？　どうした」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Good grief, I’m used to it by now... hmm? What's wrong?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「弟と妹……可愛かったなぁ……うずうず……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: My little brother and sister... they were so cute... itching to see them...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「さ、さっき見に行ったじゃろ！　こら！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Y-You just went to see them a moment ago! Hey!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: こんな人間だらけの所で一人になるな！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Don’t get alone in a place full of so many people!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ふわ……だりィ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ugh... so lazy...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ホラしゃきっと！　気合い入れろよな。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Come on, pull yourself together! Get fired up.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なんか大事そうな雰囲気だぞ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Something important seems to be happening.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「…………なんでお前まで来てんだ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...Why did you even come here?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「なんか知らないけど、でっかい作戦なんだろ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I don’t know the details, but it’s some big operation, right?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: レイが変な所に放り込まれるなら、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If Rei is thrown into some strange place,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あたしが文句言ってやるからな！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I’ll complain on her behalf!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……そりゃどーも」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...Well, thanks for that.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ふんふふんのふーん……はぐ、まぐ、むぐ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hmph hm hm hm… *nibble* *munch* *muffle*...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: んー、焼きたてパン、うまうま……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Mmm, freshly baked bread, so tasty...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あ、ああああ、ああああああ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ah, aaaaah, aaaaaah...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: パンが……パンが、異次元に消えていく……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The bread... the bread is disappearing into another dimension...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「んを？　食っちゃまずかったか？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Huh? Did I eat something I wasn’t supposed to?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「それは、ッ、一本くらい、私の……！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That would be... at least one loaf for me...!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「い、いえいえいえいえ……お客様へ、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: N-no, no, of course... it was meant for the guests...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: お出しするつもりでしたとも……おほほ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I was going to serve it... oh ho ho...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ふーん。ま、いいや。見てるなら一本食えよ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hmm. Well, fine. If you’re watching, have a loaf.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 美味いぞ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It’s delicious.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「うーん……ダメだ。確率、上がらないや。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hmm... no good. The odds aren’t improving.

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If Rei is thrown into some strange place,

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I’ll complain on her behalf!

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...Well, thanks for that.

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The bread... the bread is disappearing into another dimension...

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Huh? Did I eat something I wasn’t supposed to?

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That would be... at least one loaf for me...!

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I was going to serve it... oh ho ho...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ふーん。ま、いいや。見てるなら一本食えよ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hmm. Well, fine. If you’re watching, have a loaf.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 美味いぞ」
